cpl.description: Import *.ical calendar file exported from services like GoogleCalendar into TiddlyWiki.
cpl.name: iCal Calendar Importer
cpl.readme:
After install, drag ical file to the wiki, and put its tiddler name to the input, and make sure you fill in the same prefix as you used in your calendar widget.

A tag tiddler with name of your imported calendar will be created, each event in the calendar will add it as a tag.
